@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title Initialization and Cleanup Sequence Diagram - US263

autonumber

actor "Drone Operator" as Operator
participant "System" as System
participant "MemoryManager" as Memory
participant "DroneProcess" as Drone

activate Operator

Operator -> System: start show monitoring
activate System
System -> Memory: allocate historyOfRadar and stamps
activate Memory
Memory --> System: memory allocated
System -> Drone: spawn drone processes
activate Drone
Drone --> System: processes started
deactivate Drone
System -> System: begin collision detection loop
deactivate Memory

loop for each timestamp
    System --> System: ...(collision detection process as above)
end loop

Operator -> System: stop show monitoring
activate System
System -> Drone: send SIGCONT and wait for completion
Drone --> System: processes terminated
deactivate Drone
System -> Memory: free historyOfRadar and stamps
activate Memory
Memory --> System: memory freed
deactivate Memory
deactivate System

deactivate Operator

note right: Updated as of 11:27 AM WEST on May 16, 2025.\n- Dynamic memory management for stamps and drones_that_collied.\n- Cleanup ensures no memory leaks.

@enduml